The '''Gelion-Ascar stockade''' was a fortress built by [[Haldad]] of the [[Haladin]] to defend his people against [[Orcs]].  It was located south of [[Sarn Athrad]], between the [[Gelion]] and [[Ascar]] rivers.  It was laid siege to in the [[Battle of the Gelion-Ascar Stockade]] around {{FA|375}}, during which Haldad was killed and the stockade badly damaged.  Eventually [[Haleth]] led the Haladin away, abandoning the refuge.<ref>{{S|Men}}</ref>

